   <sect2 role="installation">
      <title>Installation de Kdeartwork</title> 
      
      <para>
         Installez <application>kdeartwork</application> avec: 
      </para> 
      
<screen><userinput>MAKEDIR=/tmp/buildkdeart &amp;&amp;
KDEART=`pwd`             &amp;&amp;
rm -rf   $MAKEDIR        &amp;&amp;
mkdir -p $MAKEDIR        &amp;&amp;
cd       $MAKEDIR        &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$TRINITY_PREFIX \
      -DCMAKE_VERBOSE_MAKEFILE=ON            \
      -DWITH_XSCREENSAVER=ON                 \
      -DWITH_LIBART=ON                       \
      -DWITH_OPENGL=ON                       \
      -DWITH_ARTS=ON                         \
      -DBUILD_ALL=ON                         \
      $KDEART            &amp;&amp;
unset KDEART MAKEDIR     &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>
      
      <para>
         Ce paquet n'est pas fourni avec une suite de tests. 
      </para> 
      
      <para>
         Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username"> root </systemitem>&nbsp;: 
         
      </para> 
      
<screen role="root">
<userinput>make install</userinput></screen>
      
   </sect2>
   
